{{Infobox broadcasting network | network_name = Gharghasht TV| network_logo = | country = {{AFG}} | network_type = [[satellite television|Satellite]] [[Television Network]]| available = [[Khost]], [[Afghanistan]]| slogan = | owner = | key_people = Sakhi Sarwar Miakhel<ref>{{cite news|url=http://surgar.aaa-int.com/-news-pg-Daily-NewS-2028.html |title=د خوست ولايت د رسنيو په ډګر کې د غرغښت په نوم يوې نوې تصويري رسنی چې د نږدې دوه مياشتو راپديخوا يې امتحاني خپرونې کولې دشنبې په ورځ دپټۍ په پريکولو سره په رسمي خپرونو پيل وکړ |date=2010-10-25 |publisher=sugar.net |language=Pashto |accessdate=16 June 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110830072315/http://surgar.aaa-int.com/-news-pg-Daily-NewS-2028.html |archivedate=30 August 2011 |df= }}</ref>| launch_date = October 23, 2010<ref name="pajhwok">{{cite news|url=http://www.pajhwok.com/ps/2010/10/23/%D9%BE%D9%87-%D8%AE%D9%88%D8%B3%D8%AA-%DA%A9%DB%90-%D8%AF-%D8%BA%D8%B1%D8%BA%DA%9A%D8%AA-%D9%BE%D9%87-%D9%86%D9%88%D9%85-%D8%A7%D8%B2%D8%A7%D8%AF-%D9%BC%D9%84%D9%88%DB%90%D8%B2%D9%8A%D9%88%D9%86-%D8%AE%D9%BE%D8%B1%D9%88%D9%86%DB%90-%D9%BE%D9%8A%D9%84-%DA%A9%DA%93%DB%90 |title=په خوست کې د غرغښت په نوم ازاد ټلوېزيون خپرونې پيل کړې |author=ميوند فد by |date=23 October 2010 |work=[[Pajhwok Afghan News]] |language=Pashto |accessdate=16 June 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120328034619/http://www.pajhwok.com/ps/2010/10/23/%D9%BE%D9%87-%D8%AE%D9%88%D8%B3%D8%AA-%DA%A9%DB%90-%D8%AF-%D8%BA%D8%B1%D8%BA%DA%9A%D8%AA-%D9%BE%D9%87-%D9%86%D9%88%D9%85-%D8%A7%D8%B2%D8%A7%D8%AF-%D9%BC%D9%84%D9%88%DB%90%D8%B2%D9%8A%D9%88%D9%86-%D8%AE%D9%BE%D8%B1%D9%88%D9%86%DB%90-%D9%BE%D9%8A%D9%84-%DA%A9%DA%93%DB%90 |archivedate=28 March 2012 |df= }}</ref>| website = | }}
'''Gharghasht TV''' ({{lang-ps|غرغښت}}) is a [[Pashto language|Pashto]] language private television station based in [[Khost]], [[Afghanistan]].<ref name="pajhwok"/> It was officially first broadcast on October 23, 2010.
The channel can also be viewed across the border in [[North Waziristan]], [[Pakistan]].<ref name="pajhwok"/>
